00:51:08,850 --> 00:51:11,493
Kadang ada luka memar.

883
00:51:12,856 --> 00:51:15,302
"kau pasti terjatuh."

884
00:51:16,193 --> 00:51:18,744
"Aku ayahmu. Aku takkan
